RedBubble Shop!

Hey you guys! For the like, 6 active followers I have on here, I wanted to let you all know that I’ve started an art shop over on redbubble. I currently have up about three prints and am slowly starting to build a collection :D

For everything that sells on my page, I earn about 20% profit or less. 

Head over to https://www.redbubble.com/people/jlinda to see more! I really appreciate your support :)

follow me on insta @j_linda99 for more updates.

summary: Alice & Vincent Alice is a loner, and her code of ethics is a bit questionable. She doesn’t mind ripping people off. In her...
caption:
Alice & Vincent

Alice is a loner, and her code of ethics is a bit questionable. She doesn’t mind ripping people off. In her mind, if they’re stupid enough to be fooled then she doesn’t mind taking advantage of that. She does have limits to what she will do. Mostly she likes spending the money she has on new technology. She knows how hard it is to make a living, so she doesn’t overspend. Most of the time ^^ Sometimes when she can’t resist she’ll make up for not having money by eating mr noodle for a month. Alice is pretty sarcastic and doesn’t have patience for most people.

Vincent on the other hand is much more simple and trusting. He has a sunny disposition and most of Alices sarcasm goes over his head. Vincent loves day dreaming of unrealistic things. He would love to fly old biplanes like his grandfather, even though he’s not too good when it comes to heights. He’s not really athletic, but super determined. Vincent loves sharing and he’s a great cook. He hates seeing Alice not eat a good meal, so whenever she let’s him, he brings her one of his creations.

Alice on the other hand connects to Vincent, because he’s one of the few genuine people that she known and she feels like he can’t fully take care of himself, so she is there to look out for him when things go south.
